### **4. 37_StreamGridFlow**  
**Description:**  
A real-time metric visualizer for multiple data streams in a grid-based chart layout.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# StreamGridFlow - Live Multi-Metric Chart

StreamGridFlow displays real-time numeric input from multiple sources using a dynamic, scrollable chart.

## Features
- Multi-stream support  
- Adjustable refresh rate  
- Built with Matplotlib  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/37_StreamGridFlow.git
cd 37_StreamGridFlow
python visualize.py
